edu.cs495.engine.game.satcollision

Class SATPolygon

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cs495.engine.game.satcollision.SATPolygon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Collidable

    public class SATPolygon
extends java.lang.Object
implements Collidable
    A polygon defined by a list of vectors. Polygons should be added clockwise (as is convention). Otherwise, calculations will be incorrect because we evaluate left-normals for SAT Collision.
    Version:
    February 2019
    Author:
    Spencer Imbleau
